text: The flag of the Cocos (Keeling) Islands was designed in 2003 and became the official flag on 6 April 2004. It was created by resident Mohammed Minkom, who had won a design contest as a teenager. This Territory is owned by Australia. ==References== ==Other websites== * Cocos (Keeling) Islands at Ausflag Category:2004 establishments in Australia
title: Flag of the Cocos (Keeling) Islands
